---
title: Middle Eastern Chicken Mezze with Honey-Glazed Haloumi, Sumac Flatbreads & Salsa
description: Turn a weeknight meal into a fun feast with this mixed platter of Middle Eastern chicken, honey-glazed haloumi, hummus and a
colourful and refreshing salsa. Sumac flatbreads add the perfect finishing touch for a feast of tasty treats where every bite is different!

*Keep an eye out... Due to recent sourcing challenges, we’ve replaced half chicken with chicken breast, which may be a little different to what’s pictured. Don’t worry, your recipe will be just as delicious!*
